window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Warriors. Lovers. Enemies. Legends.</p> <p>Their union became pivotal in Irin history, but to understand Damien and Sari's ending, you must go back to their beginning. Four hundred years ago, a young singer and a hardened warrior met and loved each other, but their life was torn apart by violence.</p> <p>But no matter how much pain and anger stain their lives, bonds in the Irin race cannot be abandoned. Damien and Sari will never truly leave each other, because those who are destined cannot be ignored.</p> <p><i>The Staff and the Blade</i> is the fourth book in the Irin Chronicles.</p>"; 
